title: Secret Society of Starfish - Dark Reflections / Waters Edge
description:
Secret Society of Starfish have been described as Tool meets Porcupine Tree, and their intricate music ranges from hard-driving to complex to ethereal instrumentals. Signed to Canadian indie label Unicorn Records, SSOS has performed with prog icons Yes, hard rockers King's X and many prog, metal and rock acts around the Midwest.
